{
  "stem": "2718.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When somebody couldn't walk it was-- it-- they, they-- if somebody couldn't walk and couldn't carry the cement, it was out of the possibilities, out of the-- there was no choice but to-- you couldn't stay in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You couldn't stay in the barrack, because they dragged you out and they beat you to death.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So you couldn't stay in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You had to go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 14 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yeah, and that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] He was in the hospital for a month.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, and I went back and he wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So in January, I, I had a bit of good luck because from, from Ujpest, we had a family there called Bushonski, and they had a shoe factory.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And in every camp block, Muhldorf as well, there was a, a barrack which was-- we had-- which had shoe repairs, and tailors, and, and also had sort of a warehouse for clothes, because people lost their clothes.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "People tore their clothes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There had to be something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was getting a little bit weak, and one day this-- one of these Bushonski said, next time they want somebody, a tailor or a shoemaker or something, you just-- because they always called out at, at appel, is there a tailor here?",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Or is there somebody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One never knew what they called out for because they called out if some-- is there-- is a musician here?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If they wanted a musician, then they picked the musician to go and clean the, the lavatories, just as a joke.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So anyway, what happened was they called out, is there a tailor around?",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
